<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN265">
      <lg type="edition" style="pūṭṭuvil">
<l>ūrnaṉi yiṟanta pārmutir paṟantalai</l>
<l>yōṅkunilai vēṅkai yoḷḷiṇar naṟuvīp</l>
<l>pōntaiyan tōṭṭiṟ puṉaintaṉar toṭuttup</l>
<l>pallāṉ kōvalar paṭalai cūṭṭak</l>
<l>kallā yiṉaiyē kaṭumāṉ ṟōṉṟal</l>
<l>vāṉēṟu puraiyuniṉ tāṇiḻal vāḻkkaip</l>
<l>paricilar celva maṉṟiyum viritārk</l>
<l>kaṭumpakaṭ ṭiyāṉai vēnta</l>
<l>roṭuṅkā veṉṟiyu niṉṉoṭu celavē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>In the wasteland where [just] earth ripens that has gone much beyond the village, (1)</l>
<l>when, as the decorators, the cowherds with many cows linked </l>
<l>palmyra fronds with fragrant blossoms from the bright clusters </l>
<l>of the high-standing kino tree [and] put on a shun shade (2-4)</l>
<l>you became a stone, appearance on a fast horse, (5)</l>
<l>while, besides the wealth of solicitors (7a-c)</l>
<l>whose living was under the shade of your foot that resembled heaven’s thunder claps, (6)</l>
<l>kings with fast high elephant bulls [and] unfolding garlands (7d-8)</l>
<l>go with you of unrestrained victory. (9)</l>
</lg>
    </div>
